response.overview: Tag teams with nfl themes in the first and only Arnold Furious Match! Straight into the Raw Bowl match where the down and out Smokin' guns fight; Yoko Zuna and Owen (the brother of the hit man) Hart, Columbian Allstars Razor Ramon & Savio Vega, and crowd favorites PSYCHO SID and 123 Kid! Big Diesel fuel, fueled Diesel fights the bulldog from Britain the British Bulldog Jake the snake, Jake Roberts fights a Native American Styled character in Tatanks and so so much more!
response.title: Terminators '96
